            <p>We believe reading should be effortless. When we have several pages to read, even the thought of getting through them could become daunting to some. Others who can read through books like a breeze might not need this service. For the majority time-pressed phone-addicted, chat-friendly text readers, this service aims to condense large amounts of text to a nice summary. </p>
            <p>This text summarization service is provided with the help of state of the art machine learning and natural language processing techniques. While you can read more about this in our <a href="https://1drv.ms/w/s!Ashlm-Nw-wnWtkN701ndJWdxfcO4">whitepaper</a>, we feel excited to inform you that this service comes from a software engineering practice. Consequently we believe you will be best served by the approach here than anywhere else.</p>
            <p>We want to give you the convenience to point to your text so we take care of processing it. Your text is used only for the purpose of generating a summary. We neither keep your text nor do we collect any information about you. Since we don't keep any information about you or your text, we merely offer you the assistant to read and condense your text. We believe you will be making a habit of using this service. When you do, you are encouraged to sign up for an account so we may help with your history.</p>
            <p>Thank you for visiting this service and happy shrinking text to gists.</p>
